## PAGE TRANSITION MECHANICS

### Content-Behind Reveal Model (Sections 0-1 transitions)

For curtain reveal and palace doors, the NEXT section content is pre-rendered BEHIND the transition overlay. The overlay moves away to reveal what is already there. This creates a natural, physical feeling.

**Key Principles:**

- Next section content is in DOM, fully rendered, positioned behind overlay
- Overlay (curtain/doors) has higher z-index
- Overlay animates away (translate/rotate)
- Content does NOT animate separately -- it is just uncovered
- After overlay off-screen: removed from DOM
- Result: buttery smooth, no flicker, no blank frames

### Curtain Reveal (Page Load -> Section 0)

- Ganesha content rendered at z-index 1, fully visible
- Curtain overlay at z-index 50, two maroon panels covering 100% viewport
- After 0.5s pause: panels translateX outward (-100% left, +100% right)
- Content visible through widening center gap as curtains part
- Duration: 2.5s, easing: cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94)
- After fully open: panels removed from DOM
- THEN shlok lines animate (staggered fade-in)
- THEN Begin button fades in

### Palace Door Opening (Section 0 -> Section 1)

- Step 1: Ganesha content fades out (0.3s)
- Step 2: Door overlay appears at z-index 40 -- two golden panels
- Step 3: Section 1 content renders behind doors at z-index 1
- Step 4: Doors swing outward -- 3D perspective(1200px) + rotateY. Left: rotateY(-110deg), Right: rotateY(110deg). transform-origin: left/right center
- Step 5: Golden radial light pours from center gap
- Step 6: 8-12 marigold petals drift from top of frame
- Step 7: Doors fully open -> removed from DOM
- Duration: 1.8s, easing: cubic-bezier(0.22, 0.61, 0.36, 1)
- Mobile fallback: fade-through-golden-light (no 3D)

### Standard Transitions (Sections 1-5)

| From -> To | Type | Duration | Details | Sec 1 -> 2 | Fade + Gold Sweep | 0.8s | Current fades, gold particles sweep L-to-R, new fades in |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Sec 2 -> 3 | Soft Cross-Fade | 0.6s | Simple fade with gold shimmer border | Sec 3 -> 4 | Fade-in Bottom | 0.5s | Current fades, new slides up 30px + fades in |
| Sec 4 -> 5 | Golden Reveal Sweep | 0.7s | Gold line sweeps L-to-R, new content revealed behind it | Nav jump | Cross-Fade | 0.4s | Quick fade for floating nav / progress dot jumps |

### Implementation Notes

- Use Framer Motion AnimatePresence for section mount/unmount
- Content-behind: position absolute stacking with z-index management
- All transitions use GPU-accelerated properties (transform, opacity)
- No layout shifts during transitions (all absolute/fixed positioning)
- prefers-reduced-motion: all transitions become simple 0.3s cross-fade

